title: Death Rattle vol. 1, 2 & 3 (Kitchen Sink)
description:
Anthology mainly consisting of horror, sci-fi and mindfuck comics

All issues published by Kitchen Sink in three volumes

Vol. 1: 3 issues published 1972-1973

Vol. 2: 18 issues published 1985-1988

Vol. 3: 5 issues published 1995-1996

Contributors included:
Richard Corben, Tom Veitch, Charles Burns, Tom Sutton, Mark Schultz, Ray Fehrenbach, Brian Biggs, Jack Jackson, Rand Holmes, Basil Wolverton, Sam Kieth, Steve Stiles, Peter Poplaski, Mike Baron, Spain Rodriguez, Jan Strnad and others
